from%20Kolkata%20to%20Imphal%20with%20173%20passengers%20on%20board%20was%20told%20to%20keep%20a%20holding%20pattern%20until%20the%20ATC%20got%20clearance%20from%20the%20security%20agencies%20-%20CISF%2C%20Bureau%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Security%20(BCAS)%2C%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20and%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Imphal%20West).%20The%20IndiGo%20flight%20remained%20in%20a%20holding%20pattern%20for%2025%20minutes%2C%20after%20which%20it%20was%20diverted%20to%20Guwahati%20in%20Assam%20at%203.03%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi-Imphal%20IndiGo%20Flight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20IndiGo%20A320%20flying%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Imphal%20with%20183%20passengers%20on%20board%20was%20diverted%20to%20Kolkata%20at%204.05%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATC%20in%20Imphal%20and%20the%20airport%20director%20alerted%20the%20Delhi%20watch%20supervisory%20officer%20(WSO)%2C%20Guwahati%20WSO%2C%20Kolkata%20WSO%2C%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20Guwahati%2C%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20in%20Silchar%2C%20the%20IAF's%20Eastern%20Air%20Command%20in%20Shillong%2C%20the%20IAF%20military%20liaison%20unit%20in%20Kolkata%3B%20Manipur%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Home%20Commissioner%2C%20BCAS%20regional%20director%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Imphal%20West)%2C%20and%20District%20Commissioner%20(Imphal%20West).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAircraft%20On%20Apron%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20flights%20-%20two%20Air%20India%20and%20an%20Indigo%20aircraft%20-%20were%20still%20parked%20on%20the%20apron%20while%20the%20airspace%20was%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fokt1fpl8_imphal-airport_625x300_19_November_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20airport%20operations%20were%20kept%20on%20hold%20till%20further%20notice%20and%20a%20NOTAM%20(Notice%20to%20Airmen)%20of%20airspace%20closure%20was%20flashed.%20A%20NOTAM%20contains%20information%20about%20the%20condition%20or%20change%20in%20any%20aeronautical%20facility%2C%20service%2C%20procedure%20or%20hazard%2C%20the%20timely%20knowledge%20of%20which%20is%20essential%20to%20personnel%20concerned%20with%20flight%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%203.55%20pm%2C%20the%20Eastern%20Air%20Command%20began%20scanning%20the%20Imphal%20airspace%20for%20threats%20till%205.35%20pm.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20Eastern%20Air%20Command%20in%20Shillong%20allowed%20Imphal%20airport%20to%20resume%20normal%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIAF%20activated%20its%20air%20defence%20response%20mechanism%20based%20on%20visual%20inputs%20from%20Imphal%20airport.%20The%20small%20object%20was%20not%20seen%20thereafter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Eastern%20Air%20Command%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20BCAS%20regional%20director%20in%20Imphal%2C%20the%20DGCA%20director%20of%20air%20safety%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20the%20Joint%20Action%20Centre%20committee%20comprising%20Manipur%20officials%20gave%20the%20go-ahead%20at%205.45%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Imphal%20ATC%20resumed%20charge%20of%20the%20airspace%20and%20aircraft%20operations%20restarted%20at%205.50%20pm.%20The%20NOTAM%20was%20subsequently%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700446320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fjvck7uhg_plane-generic_625x300_16_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funidentified-flying-object-near-imphal-airport-what-exactly-happened-4587830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controlled%20airspace%20of%20Bir%20Tikendrajit%20International%20Airport%20in%20Manipur's%20capital%20Imphal%20was%20closed%20for%20commercial%20flight%20operations%20on%20S