m%20(SJVNL)%2C%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Limited(RVNL)%2C%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHIDCL)%2C%20and%20Tehri%20Hydro%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(THDCL)%20have%20been%20assigned%20responsibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20(BRO)%20and%20the%20construction%20wing%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20have%20also%20been%20assisting%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentre%20Explores%20Five%20Alternatives%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20RVNL%20has%20commenced%20work%20on%20another%20vertical%20pipeline%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20essential%20items%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20an%20approach%20road%20by%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20in%20just%20one%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20NHIDCL%20will%20continue%20to%20drill%20from%20Silkyara%20end%20after%20working%20safety%20arrangements.%20To%20facilitate%20this%2C%20the%20Army%20has%20prepared%20the%20box%20culvert.%20A%20canopy%20framework%20is%20being%20made%20to%20ensure%20workers'%20safety.%20Work%20of%20pipeline%20laying%20will%20recommence%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Tehri%20Hydroelectric%20Development%20Corporation%20(THDC)%20will%20work%20on%20micro%20tunnelling%20from%20Barkot%20for%20which%20heavy%20machinery%20has%20already%20been%20mobilised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Sutlej%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20Limited%20(SJVNL)%20will%20do%20the%20vertical%20drilling%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20tunnel%20to%20rescue%20the%20trapped%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20ONGC%2C%20having%20expertise%20in%20deep%20drilling%2C%20has%20also%20started%20the%20initial%20work%20for%20vertical%20drilling%20from%20Barkot%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERace%20To%20Rescue%20Trapped%20Workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20an%20agonising%20wait%20for%20the%20families%20keeping%20vigil%20outside%20the%20tunnel.%20Their%20voices%20are%20getting%20weaker%2C%20their%20strength%20seemingly%20dimming%2C%20family%20members%20said%20after%20speaking%20to%20some%20of%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20are%20being%20provided%20food%2C%20water%20and%20oxygen%20supply%20as%20rescue%20teams%20work%20overtime%20for%20a%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20yesterday%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20tunnel%20collapse.%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said%20the%20priority%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20workers%20alive.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20auger%20machine%20works%20properly%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20them%20in%20the%20next%202-2.5%20days.%20Roads%20are%20being%20made%20by%20BRO%20(Border%20Roads%20Organisition)%20to%20bring%20in%20special%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20have%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20prolonged%20confinement%20may%20necessitate%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%20recovery%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2041%20workers%20have%20been%20stuck%20since%20last%20Sunday%20after%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel%20caved%20in.%20Officials%20said%20that%20all%20workers%20are%20safe%20and%20are%20being%20supplied%20food%20and%20water%20through%20steel%20pipes%20that%20have%20been%20drilled%20into%20the%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%2C%20a%20national%20infrastructure%20initiative%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%2C%20and%20Yamunotri.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700445300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fn4m2ga8g_uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue_625x300_20_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-utta