ect%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20flying%20object%26quot%3B%20and%20activated%20their%20air%20defence%20response%20mechanism.%20Flight%20operations%20resumed%20after%20clearance%20from%20the%20IAF.%20The%20incident%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20investigated%20separately%20by%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20and%20defence%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22KANGKAN%20KALITA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fufo-sparks-3-hour-imphal-airspace-closure%2Farticleshow%2F105340146.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Argentina's%20Trump-like%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20who%20proposed%20making%20the%20US%20dollar%20the%20country's%20official%20currency%2C%20wins%20election%20after%20his%20opponent%20concedes%20defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Javier%20Milei%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655aa00c4ca513d8242bffa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresidential%20candidate%20of%20the%20Liberty%20Advances%20coalition%20Javier%20Milei%20arrives%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20presidential%20runoff%20election%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Sunday%2C%20Nov.%2019%2C%202023.%3Cp%3E(AP%20Photo%2FMatias%20Delacroix)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20self-described%20%26quot%3Banarcho-capitalist%26quot%3B%20candidate%20often%20compared%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20claimed%20victory%20in%20Argentina's%20presidential%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJavier%20Milei's%20win%20comes%20as%20his%20opponent%2C%20Argentina's%20Economy%20Minister%20Sergio%20Massa%2C%20conceded%20defeat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20a%20Milei%20victory%2C%20the%20country%20will%20swing%20to%20the%20right%20amid%20discontent%20over%20soaring%20inflation%20and%20rising%20poverty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArgentina's%20Economy%20Minister%20Sergio%20Massa%20conceded%20defeat%20to%20populist%20Javier%20Milei%20in%20Sunday's%20fiercely%20polarized%20presidential%20runoff%20even%20before%20the%20country's%20electoral%20authority%20released%20official%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassa%20congratulated%20his%20opponent%2C%20a%20right-wing%20economist%20who%20has%20promised%20a%20dramatic%20shake-up%20for%20many%20of%20the%20nation's%20institutions%20and%20welcomed%20frequent%20comparisons%20of%20him%20to%20former%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20Massa's%20concession%20speech%2C%20the%20Argentine%20electoral%20authority%20released%20partial%20results%3A%20With%2086.6%25%20of%20votes%20tallied%2C%20Milei%20had%2055.95%25%20and%20Massa%2044.04%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20Milei%20victory%2C%20the%20country%20will%20swing%20to%20the%20right%20amid%20discontent%20over%20soaring%20inflation%20and%20rising%20poverty%2C%20and%20empower%20a%20freshman%20lawmaker%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20an%20anarcho-capitalist%20and%20got%20his%20start%20as%20a%20television%20talking%20head%20blasting%20what%20he%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20caste.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20has%20soared%20above%20140%25%20and%20poverty%20has%20worsened%20while%20Massa%20has%20held%20his%20post.%20Milei%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fjavier-milei-argentina-elections-presidency-54671463bcf1a3ef22e7f7a2a602adcd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20self-described%20anarcho-capitalist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20proposed%20to%20slash%20the%20size%20of%20the%20state%20and%20rein%20in%20inflation%2C%20while%20the%20government%20minister%20he%20was%20running%20against%20warned%20people%20about%20the%20negative%20impacts%20of%20such%20policies.%20The%20election%20forced%20many%20to%20decide%20which%20of%20the%20two%20they%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20least%20bad%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilei's%20screeds%20resonated%20widely%20with%20Argentines%20angered%20by%20their%20struggle%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20particularly%20young%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20covers%20less%20and%20less%20each%20day.%20I'm%20a%20qualified%20individual%2C%20and%20my%20salary%20isn't%20enough%20for%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Esteban%20Medina%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20physical%20therapist%20from%20Ezeiza%2C%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20Milei%20rally%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassa%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20figures%20in%20a%20deeply%20unpopular%20administration%2C%20was%20once%20seen%20as%20having%20little%20chance%20of%20victory.%20But%20he%20managed%20to%20mobilize%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fargentina-election-peronism-massa-milei-f5db5a92328f4316384ff6e0092c5272%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20networks%20of%20his%20Peronist%20party%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20clinched%20a%20decisive%20first-place%20finish%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20campaign%20cautioned%20Argentines%20that%20his%20libertarian%20opponent's%20plan%20to%20eliminate%20key%20ministries%20and%20otherwise%20sharply%20curtail%20the%20state%20would%20threaten%20public%20services%2C%20including%20health%20and%20education%2C%20and%20welfare%20programs%20many%20rely%20on.%20Massa%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20his%20opponent's%20often%20aggressive%20rhetoric%20and%20openly%20questioned%20his%20mental%20acuity%3B%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20round%2C%20Milei%20sometimes%20carried%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmilei-argentina-chainsaw-fed35a37c6137b951e4adada3d866436%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevving%20chainsaw%20at%20rallies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20casting%20her%20vote%20at%20the%20stately%20University%20of%20Buenos%20Aires%20Law%20School%2C%20Jenifer%20Pio%2C%2036%2C%20told%20the%20AP%20that%20she%20fears%20a%20Milei%20victory%20would%20risk%20the%20return%20of%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMilei%20doesn't%20have%20the%20faintest%20idea%20of%20how%20to%20govern%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pio%2C%20a%20homemaker.%20%26quot%3BIt%20isn't%20bad%20that%20he's%20prideful%2C%20but%20he%20would%20need%20to%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20stability.%20He's%20unstable%20emotionally%20and%20psychologically.%20He's%20unwell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAna%20Iparraguirre%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20pollster%20GBAO%20Strategies%2C%20said%20Massa's%20%26quot%3Bonly%20chance%20to%20win%20this%20election%20when%20people%20want%20change%20...%20is%20to%20make%20this%20election%20a%20referendum%20on%20whether%20Milei%20is%20fit%20to%20be%20president%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20starting%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20Argentina%2C%20and%20this%20chapter%20requires%20not%20only%20goodwill%2C%20intelligence%20and%20capability%20but%20above%20all%2C%20dialogue%20and%20the%20necessary%20consensus%20for%20our%20homeland%20to%20traverse%20a%20much%20more%20virtuous%20path%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Massa%20told%20journalists%20Sunday%20after%20casting%20his%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilei%20accused%20Massa%20and%20his%20allies%20of%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bcampaign%20of%20fear%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20walked%20back%20some%20of%20his%20most%20controversial%20proposals%2C%20such%20as%20loosening%20gun%20control.%20In%20his%20final%20campaign%20ad%2C%20Milei%20looks%20at%20the%20camera%20and%20assures%20voters%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20privatize%20education%20or%20health%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20great%20job%20despite%20the%20fear%20campaign%20and%20all%20the%20dirty%20tactics%20they%20used%20against%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Milei%20told%20journalists%20after%20he%20voted%20amid%20a%20large%20security%20operation%20as%20dozens%20of%20supporters%20and%20journalists%20gathered%20at%20his%20polling%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20supporters%20is%20Mar%C3%ADa%20Gabriela%20Gaviola%2C%20a%2063-year-old%20entrepreneur%20doing%20everything%20she%20can%20to%20avoid%20shuttering%20her%20company%2C%20which%20manufactures%20veterinary%20products%2C%20amid%20surging%20prices%20for%20materials.%20And%20the%20government%20hasn't%20helped%2C%20including%20Massa%20who%20has%20held%20his%20ministerial%20post%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20productive%20sector%20of%20this%20country%20isn't%20considered.%20How%20long%20can%20a%20country%20that%20doesn't%20produce%20be%20OK%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Gaviola%2C%20who%20has%20taken%20on%20two%20side%20jobs%20to%20keep%20her%20company%20afloat.%20%26quot%3BTruth%20is%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20Milei.%20I've%20heard%20him%20a%20bit.%20I%20don't%20know%20him%2C%20but%20the%20one%20who%20I%20already%20know%20doesn't%20help%20me.%20I%20prefer%20to%20try%20something%20new.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20pre-election%20polls%2C%20which%20have%20been%20notoriously%20wrong%20at%20every%20step%20of%20this%20year's%20campaign%2C%20showed%20a%20statistical%20tie%20between%20the%20two%20candidates.%20Voters%20for%20first-round%20candidates%20who%20didn't%20make%20the%20runoff%20will%20be%20key.%20Patricia%20Bullrich%2C%20who%20placed%20third%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fargentina-bullrich-milei-massa-macri-9b12de37be6e17cf5c7c477fcfd67c66%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20Milei%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20bitter%20division%20this%20campaign%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20Milei%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fargentina-milei-runoff-massa-d2c5a204bcc601e099b69c532e11829f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%20both%20jeers%20and%20cheers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20night%20