iotics%20unavailable.%20Missions%20were%20being%20planned%20to%20evacuate%20the%20remaining%20people%20to%20southern%20Gaza%20in%20the%20next%2024-72%20hours%2C%20%26quot%3Bpending%20guarantees%20of%20safe%20passage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20Sunday%2C%20Israel's%20army%20said%20it%20had%20strong%20evidence%20supporting%20its%20claims%20that%20Hamas%20maintains%20a%20sprawling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-hamas-war-shifa-hospital-ce8fda9821a011a6cb6e4a3df5c90916%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommand%20post%20inside%20and%20under%20Shifa%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Israel%20has%20portrayed%20the%20hospital%20as%20a%20key%20target%20in%20its%20war%20to%20end%20Hamas'%20rule%20in%20Gaza%20following%20the%20militant%20group's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-hamas-attack-military-war-a8f63b07641212f0de61861844e5e71e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewide-ranging%20attack%20into%20southern%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20six%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20it%20found%20a%2055-meter%20(60-yard)%20tunnel%20about%2010%20meters%20under%20the%20hospital's%2020-acre%20complex%2C%20which%20includes%20several%20buildings%2C%20garages%20and%20a%20plaza.%20It%20said%20the%20tunnel%20included%20a%20staircase%2C%20blast-proof%20door%2C%20and%20a%20firing%20hole%20that%20could%20be%20used%20by%20snipers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%20couldn't%20independently%20verify%20Israel's%20findings%2C%20which%20included%20security%20camera%20video%20showing%20what%20the%20military%20said%20were%20two%20foreign%20hostages%2C%20one%20Thai%20and%20one%20Nepalese%2C%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20following%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20also%20said%20an%20independent%20medical%20report%20had%20determined%20that%20a%20female%20Israeli%20soldier%2C%20Cpl.%20Noa%20Marciano%2C%20whose%20body%20was%20recovered%20in%20Gaza%20last%20week%2C%20had%20been%20killed%20by%20Hamas%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Marciano%20had%20earlier%20been%20injured%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20Nov.%209%20that%20killed%20her%20captor%2C%20according%20to%20Israel's%20intelligence%20assessment.%20The%20injuries%20were%20not%20life-threatening%20but%20she%20was%20then%20killed%20by%20a%20Hamas%20militant%20in%20Shifa%2C%20the%20army%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20and%20hospital%20staff%20earlier%20denied%20the%20allegations%20of%20a%20command%20post%20under%20Shifa.%20Critics%20describe%20the%20hospital%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20what%20they%20call%20Israel's%20reckless%20endangerment%20of%20civilians.%20Thousands%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20and%20there%20are%20severe%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20medicine%20and%20fuel%20in%20the%20besieged%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20Hamas%20official%20Osama%20Hamdan%20dismissed%20the%20Israeli%20military's%20announcement%20and%20didn't%20deny%20that%20Gaza%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-hamas-tunnels-warfare-15453b5729e38aeb55af5b419835a5eb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20kilometers%20of%20tunnels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Israelis%20said%20there%20was%20a%20command%20and%20control%20center%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20greater%20than%20just%20a%20tunnel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F31-premature-babies-taken-out-of-gaza-city-safety-egypt-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700436964000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655a9b2922cf74a57399e866%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F31-premature-babies-taken-out-of-gaza-city-sa