%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20are%20close%20to%20reaching%20a%20deal%20agreeing%20to%20a%20five-day%20%E2%80%9Cpause%E2%80%9D%20in%20fighting%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2023%2F11%2F18%2Fus-israel-hamas-reach-tentative-deal-pause-conflict-free-dozens-hostages%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%20This%20pause%20would%20reportedly%20be%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20dozens%20of%20women%20and%20children%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20are%20currently%20in%20talks%20mediated%20by%20Qatar%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20detailed%2C%20six-page%20set%20of%20written%20terms%20would%20require%20all%20parties%20to%20the%20conflict%20to%20freeze%20combat%20operations%20for%20at%20least%20five%20days%20while%20an%20initial%2050%20or%20more%20hostages%20are%20released%20in%20smaller%20batches%20every%2024%20hours.%20It%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20many%20of%20the%20239%20people%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20captivity%20in%20Gaza%20would%20be%20released%20under%20the%20deal.%20Overhead%20surveillance%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Ewould%20monitor%20movement%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20police%20the%20pause%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20US%20daily%20stated.%20The%20pause%20is%20also%20supposed%20to%20allow%20substantial%20humanitarian%20relief%20into%20Gaza.%20Earlier%2C%20a%20Hamas%20negotiator%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Hamas%20would%20not%20agree%20to%20overhead%20surveillance%20or%20any%20other%20movement%20in%20the%20skies%20during%20the%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20Adrienne%20Watson%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20there%20was%20no%20final%20deal%20yet%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20get%20a%20deal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20political%20bureau%20and%20presently%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20international%20relations%20office%20in%20Doha%2C%20Dr%20Musa%20Abu%20Marzouq%2C%20has%20given%20extensive%20details%20of%20the%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20are%20negotiating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20will%20release%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20return%20for%20Israel%20releasing%20100%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20Marzouq%20said.%C2%A0He%20said%20there%20were%20two%20conditions.%20First%2C%20Hamas%20wants%20free%20movement%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20to%20move%20both%20north-to-south%20and%20south-to-north.%20He%20said%20Israel%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20north-south%20movement%20but%20is%20so%20far%20not%20agreeing%20to%20the%20south-north%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarzouq%20said%20the%20second%20condition%20is%20that%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20airstrikes%20completely%20stopping%20during%20the%20five-day%20ceasefire%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20movement%20in%20the%20skies%2C%20i.e.%20no%20reconnaissance%20flights%20or%20drones.%20So%20far%20Israel%20has%20not%20agreed%20to%20this%20condition%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAGL3mkKQ8ng%3Fsi%3DZ7WiAoqb7SQI8bF5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20continues%20to%20draw%20condemnation%20from%20international%20organisations.%20United%20Nations%20Secretary%20General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20on%20Sunday%20released%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20strikes%20on%20two%20UNRWA%20schools%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20are%20seeking%20shelter%20at%20United%20Nations%20facilities%20throughout