.%20Patients%20and%20health%20staff%20with%20whom%20they%20spoke%20were%20terrified%20for%20their%20safety%20and%20health%2C%20and%20pleaded%20for%20evacuation.%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20can%20no%20longer%20admit%20patients%2C%20with%20the%20injured%20and%20sick%20now%20being%20directed%20to%20the%20seriously%20overwhelmed%20and%20barely%20functioning%20Indonesian%20Hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20visit%2C%2031%20prematurely%20born%20babies%20have%20been%20evacuated%20from%20al-Shifa%20Hospital%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20European%20and%20Nasser%20hospitals%20in%20the%20south%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2023%2F11%2F19%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-israel-attacked-two-schools-killing-dozens%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Two%20babies%20died%20before%20they%20could%20be%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20have%20been%20raiding%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20for%20days%20now%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F16%2Fisrael-gaza-shifa-hamas-evidence%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20not%20found%20any%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20corroborate%20its%20claims%20that%20the%20hospital%20sits%20on%20top%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20headquarters.%20The%20hospital%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20severe%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20water%20and%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700417832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19234620%2FF_P_zHFX0AAX0nd.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-hamas-close-to-agreeing-on-five-day-pause-in-fighting-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20pause%20would%20reportedly%20be%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20dozens%20of%20women%20and%20children%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fw