jay%20Pahalwan%20(52)%20is%20named%20in%2024%20cases%2C%20including%20murder%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20and%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20was%20announced%20on%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Crime)%20RS%20Yadav%20said%20a%20team%20of%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20was%20tasked%20to%20arrest%20people%20who%20are%20named%20in%20cases%20of%20heinous%20crimes%20and%20were%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInformation%20from%20police%20and%20judicial%20records%20was%20gathered.%20Complete%20criminal%20records%20of%20the%20accused%20maintained%20in%20numerous%20police%20files%2C%20SCRB%20records%2C%20and%20concerned%20trial%20courts%20were%20analysed.%20From%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20records%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20a%20proclaimed%20offender%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20was%20hiding%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20officials%20said%20after%20tracing%20Pahalwan's%20location%2C%20a%20special%20team%20was%20formed%20and%20dispatched%20to%20Jabalpur%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202011%2C%20he%20(Pahalwan)%20had%20murdered%20Raghuvir%20Singh%20(69)%20after%20abducting%20him%20from%20the%20Kishangarh%20area%20of%20Delhi.%20He%20took%20the%20victim%20to%20the%20Andheri%20Mor%20area%20in%20Delhi%20where%20he%20asked%20him%20to%20give%20his%20plot.%20When%20the%20victim%20refused%2C%20he%20shot%20him%20and%20dumped%20his%20body%20in%20a%20forest%20area%20near%20DLF%20Phase-II%20in%20Gurugram%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20arrest%2C%20Pahalwan%20disclosed%20that%20he%20had%20got%20parole%20of%20two%20days%20in%20April%202018%20and%20he%20jumped%20it%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20name%20Vikram%20Singh%2C%20the%20accused%20started%20working%20at%20a%20'pehalwani%20akhara'%20in%20Kolhapur%20in%20Maharashtra.%20He%20met%20a%20woman%20while%20his%20stay%20there%2C%20and%20after%20two%20years%2C%20moved%20to%20Raipur%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20he%20started%20a%20property%20business%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20in%20Raipur%2C%20Pahalwan%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20his%20friends%20and%20one%20of%20them%20asked%20him%20to%20start%20a%20property%20business%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%20they%20said.%20He%20moved%20his%20business%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20city%20after%20operating%20for%20two%20years%20in%20Raipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20one%20year%2C%20he%20was%20running%20his%20property%20business%20in%20Jabalpur.%20He%20used%20to%20buy%20land%2C%20villas%20and%20farms%2C%20and%20sell%20these%20at%20higher%20prices%2C%20earning%20huge%20profits.%20He%20has%20a%20farmhouse%20in%20the%20Jabalpur%20area%2C%20wherein%2C%20he%20had%20employed%2014%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20special%20commissioner%20of%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20that%20Pahalwan%20had%20employed%20four%20armed%20bodyguards%20for%20his%20safety.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20two%20sons%20and%20both%20are%20lawyers%2C%20who%20indulged%20in%20'pairvi'%20of%20criminal%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20the%20cases%20Pahalwan%20is%20named%20in%20also%20include%20those%20related%20to%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20theft%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%20and%20the%20Arms%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700414940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia