0Gill%20for%20137%20off%20120%20balls%2C%20with%2015%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes.%20Australia%20was%20239%2F4%20in%2042.5%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20clinched%20their%20sixth%20World%20Cup%20title%2C%20with%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20hitting%20the%20winning%20runs%20with%20seven%20overs%20and%20six%20wickets%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20took%20two%20wickets%20while%20Shami%20took%20a%20wicket.%20Siraj%20took%20a%20wicket%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20and%20KL%20Rahul's%20gritty%20half-centuries%20powered%20India%20to%20240%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20at%20Ahmedabad's%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20put%20on%20a%20stunning%20display%20of%20tight%20and%20belligerent%20bowling%20to%20bundle%20out%20India%20for%20240%20after%20pacers%20Mitchell%20Starc%2C%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20and%20Pat%20Cummins%20broke%20the%20back%20of%20the%20hosts'%20batting%20line-ups%20early%20in%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20scored%20the%20most%20for%20India%20with%2066%20runs%20off%20107%20deliveries%2C%20while%20Kohli%20played%20a%20fine%20knock%20of%2054%20runs%20after%20Rohit%20Sharma's%2047-run%20knock%20set%20a%20solid%20platform%20for%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPut%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20Rohit%20got%20off%20to%20a%20fast%20start%2C%20hitting%20a%20four%20and%20a%20six%20in%20the%20first%20over%20and%20a%20six%20and%20four%20in%20the%20fourth.%20Even%20when%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20was%20under%20pressure%2C%20Mitchell%20Starc%20struck%20in%20the%20fifth%20over%20as%20he%20removed%20Shubman%20Gill%20for%20four%20runs.%20A%20mistimed%20front%20foot%20pull%20brought%20the%20end%20of%20Gill's%20stay%20at%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flood%20of%20runs%20continued%20as%20Virat%20Kohli%20set%20his%20sights%20early%20on%20Starc%20and%20blasted%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20fours.%20However%2C%20India's%20aggressive%20streak%20was%20cut%20short%20again%