0hate%20group%C2%A0%26quot%3BBlood%20Tribe%26quot%3B%20marched%20in%20downtown%20Madison%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20say%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A126%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneo-nazis-chanted-there-will-be-blood-in-madison-wisconsin%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20Plight%20Is%20Testament%20to%20the%20Kismet%20of%20Women%20Politicians%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19194524%2FF8yrxWKa0AAYIV9.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20parliament%20finally%20passed%20a%20law%20reserving%20one-third%20of%20total%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20and%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20every%20state%2C%20the%20targeting%20of%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20unsubstantiated%20charges%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20%E2%80%98gender%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98performance%20of%20femininity%E2%80%99%20shape%20the%20life%20of%20women%20leaders%20across%20the%20political%20sphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20observe%20the%20statistics%20first.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2Frs%2Fmembers%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20only%2031%20women%20among%20239%20total%20members%20and%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F164.100.47.194%2Floksabha%2FMembers%2Fwomen.aspx%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20only%2082%20of%20the%20539%20members%20are%20women.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.gov.in%2Fmy-government%2Fwhos-who%2Fcouncil-ministers%5C%22%3EGovernment%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20only%2010%20women%20find%20representation%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2079-member%20council%20of%20ministers%2C%20out%20of%20which%20only%20two%20hold%C2%A0%20cabinet%20rank.%20The%20picture%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D1882226%5C%22%3Estate%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20bleaker%2C%20with%20the%20national%20average%20of%20women%20in%20state%20assemblies%20being%20around%209%25.%20India%E2%80%99s%20rank%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.weforum.org%2Fdocs%2FWEF_GGGR_2023.pdf%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20Global%20Gender%20Gap%20Index%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20127%20out%20of%20146%2C%20with%20the%20country%20trailing%20behind%20neighbours%20like%20Bangladesh%2C%20Nepal%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20general%20election%2C%20out%20of%20the%20435%20candidates%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20fielded%2C%2012.6%25%20were%20women.%20Women%20constituted%2012.9%25%20of%20the%20total%20candidates%20fielded%20by%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20regional%20parties%E2%80%99%20selection%20of%20women%20candidates%20was%20quite%20commendable.%20Of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20candidates%20fielded%20by%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20All-India%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%2037.1%25%20were%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvidently%2C%20what%20are%20typically%20viewed%20as%20%E2%80%98gender%20neutral%E2%80%99%20public%20institutions%20and%20political%20parties%20in%20India%20are%20exclusively%20%E2%80%98for%2C%20by%20and%20of%E2%80%99%20men.%20Rather%2C%20%E2%80%98masculinity%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20defining%20feature%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20On%20its%20own%2C%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Act%2C%202023%20cannot%20enable%20greater%20political%20participation%20of%20women%20and%20their%20equal%20representation%20in%20parliament%20and%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Treatment%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Is%20a%20Case%20Study%20on%20Gender%2C%20Power%20and%20Politics%20in%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-treatment-of-mahua-moitra-is-a-case-study-on-gender-power-and-politics-in-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Treatment%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Is%20a%20Case%20Study%20on%20Gender%2C%20Power%20and%20Politics%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Futorontopress.com%2F9781487525200%2Fwomen-power-and-political-representation%2F%5C%22%3Ebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%20%3Cem%3EWomen%2C%20Power%2C%20and%20Political%20Representation%3A%20Canadian%20and%20Comparative%20Perspectives%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20authors%20have%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20introduction%20of%20gender%20quotas%20has%20improved%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20Canadian%20politics.%20However%2C%20Canadian%20women%20still%20face%20many%20informal%20and%20formal%20barriers%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20when%20they%20seek%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20political%20power%20but%20also%20once%20they%20have%20gained%20that%20power.%20They%20have%20cautioned%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwomen%20need%20not%20just%20be%20present%20in%20politics%2C%20but%20rather%20should%20have%20access%20to%20key%20positions%20of%20power%20where%20they%20can%20act%20as%20gatekeepers%2C%20agenda%20setters%2C%20and%20political%20insiders%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Moitra%20matter%20reinforces%20the%20same%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20politics%20has%20constructed%20a%20sexual%20imagery%20of%20women%20leaders%20that%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20their%20character%2C%20physical%20appearance%2C%20dress%2C%20demeanour%20and%20family.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fwomen-politicians-face-sexism-and-misogynism-in-the-boys-club%2F%5C%22%3EThey%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20closely%20watched%20and%20their%20performance%20minutely%20scrutinised.%20While%20their%20success%20is%20understated%20and%20mostly%20shoved%20under%20the%20carpet%2C%20their%20failure%20is%20wholly%20attributed%20to%20their%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20news%20reporting%20on%20women%20MPs%20like%20Moitra%20is%20pervaded%20by%20gendered%20perceptions%20of%20ambition%2C%20visibility%2C%20competitiveness%2C%20suitability%20and%20capability.%20Her%20association%20with%20a%20leading%20businessman%20and%20fight%20with%20an%20ex-lover%20over%20Henry%2C%20their%20pet%20dog%2C%20have%20become%20more%20newsworthy%20than%20her%20attendance%20and%20performance%20in%20parliament.%20Conversely%2C%20her%20participation%20in%20parliamentary%20debates%2C%20the%20type%20of%20questions%20she%20has%20raised%2C%20and%20the%20veracity%20of%20her%20criticisms%20of%20the%20kleptocratic%20tendencies%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20have%20been%20largely%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20those%20pillorying%20Moitra%20have%20bothered%20to%20analyse%20how%20many%20of%20questions%20she%20has%20raised%20in%20Parliament%20have%20a%20direct%20link%20with%20her%20businessman%20friend%2C%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%2C%20whose%20office%20staff%20helped%20her%20upload%20those%20questions.%20When%20it%20is%20common%20practice%20for%20MPs%20to%20share%20their%20login%20details%20and%20even%20one-time-passwords%20(OTPs)%20with%20personal%20assistants%2C%20office%20staff%2C%20policy%20clerks%2C%20interns%20and%20others%20%E2%80%93%20the%20authors%20and%20almost%20all%20LAMP%20fellows%20who%20have%20worked%20with%20MPs%20from%20different%20political%20parties%20will%20easily%20vouch%20for%20this%20fact%20%E2%80%93%20why%20is%20Mahua%20Moitra%20being%20singled%20out%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%202015%20to%20oversee%20the%20moral%20and%20ethical%20conduct%20of%20members%20and%20examine%20cases%20of%20misconduct%20referred%20to%20it%2C%20has%20been%20operating%20without%20a%20proper%20written%20%E2%80%98Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20Members%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20mandatory%20%E2%80%98Declaration%20of%20Members%E2%80%99%20Business%20Interests%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20highly%20probable%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20these%20two%20important%20documents%2C%20the%20committee%20can%20cherry-pick%20cases%20involving%20MPs%20from%20opposition%20parties%20while%20going%20easy%20with%20ruling%20party%20members.%20Further%2C%20the%20committee%20can%20also%20conduct%20hearings%20without%20following%20a%20fair%2C%20just%20and%20impartial%20procedure%20%E2%80%93%20as%20was%20seen%20in%20the%20Moitra%20matter%2C%20where%20she%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20cross-examine%20those%20who%20had%20levelled%20grave%20charges%20against%20her.%20This%20violates%20the%20norms%20of%20natural%20justice%20in%20a%20constitutional%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-ramesh-bidhuri-very-different-parliament-committee%5C%22%3Enot%20escaped%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20notice%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20committee%20has%20been%20super%20swift%20to%20investigate%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20association%20with%20Hiranandani.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20its%20response%20has%20been%20extremely%20tardy%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20conduct%20of%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20who%20made%20communal%20and%20sexist%20comments%20against%20several%20MPs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3Eincluding%20Danish%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20avert%20sexual%20objectification%2C%20increase%20their%20acceptability%20within%20politics%20and%20be%20%E2%80%98likeable%E2%80%99%20among%20the%20masses%2C%20women%20leaders%20have%20taken%20to%20supposedly%20asexual%2C%20respectable%20and%20dignified%20titles%20like%20%E2%80%98Didi%E2%80%99%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20(elder%20sister)%2C%20%E2%80%98Behenji%E2%80%99%20Mayawati%20(sister)%2C%20%E2%80%98Amma%E2%80%99%20Jayalalitha%20(mother).%20Even%20Moitra%20has%20chanted%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Ma%20Durga%E2%80%99%20and%20invoked%20the%20powerful%20Hindu%20goddess%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMahuaMoitra%2Fstatus%2F1715080166870004009%5C%22%3EX%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fight%20off%20the%20attacks%20on%20herself%20from%20the%20BJP.%20We%20cannot%20forget%20that%20as%20a%20woman%20politician%2C%20she%20has%20to%20work%20over%20time%20to%20not%20let%20the%20scandal%20blight%20her%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20the%20Question%20of%20Maryada%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-and-the-question-of-maryada%5C%22%3EMahua%20Moitra%20and%20the%20Question%20of%20Maryada%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20there%20exists%20zero%20female%20sorority%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20Women%20politicians%20do%20not%20get%20the%20requisite%20support%20from%20peers%20in%20their%20own%20political%20party%2C%20nor%20are%20formal%20institutional%20mechanisms%20available%20to%20check%20misogyny%20and%20bullying.%20When%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20quizzed%20MP%20Moitra%20about%20her%20private%20life%2C%20none%20of%20the%20women%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20responded.%20Women%20leaders%20find%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20support%20their%20ilk%20across%20party%20lines%20because%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20reconcile%20their%20gender%20identity%20and%20political%20differences.%20Explaining%20the%20reality%20of%20female%20misogyny%2C%20feminist%20writer%20Chimamanda%20Adichie%20has%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BA%5Dnd%20there%20are%20many%20women%20in%20the%20world%20who%20do%20not%20like%20other%20women.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20writ%20large%20in%20Indian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIreland%E2%80%99s%20landmark%202009%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.oireachtas.ie%2Fie%2Foireachtas%2Fcommittee%2Fdail%2F32%2Fjoint_committee_on_justice_and_equality%2Freports%2F2009%2F2009-11-05_women-s-participation-in-politics_en.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Women%E2%80%99s%20Participation%20in%20Politics%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20found%20that%20factors%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98less%20confidence%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98gendered%20culture%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98gender%20bias%20in%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%20in%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20selection%20procedures%E2%80%99%20adversely%20affect%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.womenforelection.ie%2Fpdfs%2F5Cs-Scorecard-assessing-progress-in-the-wake-of-the-2009-Womens-Participation-in-Politics-report.pdf%5C%22%3Epoliticians%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Particularly%20in%20India%2C%20because%20the%20Parliament%2C%20state%20assemblies%20and%20political%20parties%20are%20mainly%20led%20and%20run%20by%20men%2C%20the%20culture%20of%20behaviour%20and%20the%20informally%20accepted%20norms%20of%20language%2C%20views%20and%20expressions%20render%20the%20political%20sphere%20unsuitable%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoitra%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fparliamentary-ethics-committee-opposition-mps-mahua-moitra%5C%22%3Elashed%20out%20against%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20unfair%20procedure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20manner%20of%20investigation%20and%20content%20of%20the%20questions.%20While%20people%20were%20left%20aghast%20at%20her%20audacity%2C%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20has%20called%20her%20remarks%20%E2%80%98explosive%E2%80%99.%20Kimberle%20Crenshaw%E2%80%99s%20words%20can%20be%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20Indian%20society%20for%20which%20%E2%80%9Csaving%20honour%20from%20shame%20is%20a%20priority.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20priority%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20readily%20interpreted%20as%20obliging%20women%20not%20to%20scream%20rather%20than%20obliging%20men%20not%20to%20hit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20a%20deep-seated%20culture%20of%20misogyny%2C%20what%20will%20it%20take%20for%20Indian%20lawmakers%20to%20remodel%20Parliament%20into%20a%20truly%20diverse%2C%20inclusive%20and%20accommodating%20place%20of%20work%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrerna%20Dhoop%20is%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%20at%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%20(NLSIU)%20Bangalore%20and%20Vandana%20Dhoop%20teaches%20at%20the%20St.%20Xavier%E2%80%99s%20University%2C%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700403374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19194524%2FF8yrxWKa0AAYIV9.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmahua-moitras-plight-is-testament-to-the-kismet-of-women-politicians-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20politics%20has%20constructed%20a%20sexual%20imagery%20of%20women%20leaders%20that%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20their%20character%2C%20physical%20appearance%2C%20dress%2C%20demeanour%20and%20family.%20While%20their%20success%20is%20understated%20and%20mostly%20shoved%20under%20the%20carpet%2C%20their%20failure%20is%20wholly%20attributed%20to%20their%20gender.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmahua-moitras-plight-is-testament-to-the-kismet-of-women-politicians-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20cheer%20for%20India%20in%20Team%20India%20jerseys!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700402974000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105335015%2Cimgsize-119758.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoor-alia-bhatt-ajay-devgn-kajol-celebs-cheer-for-india-in-team-india-jerseys%2Farticleshow%2F105335008.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105335008.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20celebs%20who've%20sported%20the%20Indian%20t