0%93%20after%20they%20seized%20power%20in%20February%202021%2C%20the%20coup%20leaders%20indicated%20surprise%20when%20the%20coup%20met%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwhy-myanmar-is-rising-up-in-collective-fury-after-a-military-coup-the-conversation-weekly-podcast-154991%5C%22%3Ewidespread%20outrage%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sustained%20public%20protest%20and%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20quell%20opposition%2C%20military%20bosses%20have%20adopted%20a%20strategy%20of%20arbitrary%20arrest%20and%20extreme%20violence.%20The%20Assistance%20Association%20for%20Political%20Prisoners%20estimates%2019%2C675%20people%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoup.aappb.org%2F%5C%22%3Ecurrently%20jailed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20figure%20which%20increases%20almost%20daily.%20Peaceful%20protests%20are%20met%20with%20army%20snipers%20and%20shoot-to-kill%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%E2%80%99s%20military%20routinely%20responds%20to%20armed%20resistance%20by%20collectively%20punishing%20nearby%20civilian%20populations.%20This%20has%20included%20devastating%20airstrikes%20on%20civilian%20targets%20and%20scorched-earth%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fculture%2Fbooks%2Fthe-quality-of-mercy-in-myanmar.html%5C%22%3Eclearance%20operation%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20campaigns%20that%20have%20killed%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20displaced%20more%20than%20700%2C000%20more.%20Rather%20than%20cowing%20the%20populace%2C%20junta%20violence%20continues%20to%20spur%20nationwide%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F559671%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231115-22-m3te4e.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26q%3D45%26auto%3Dformat%26w%3D1000%26fit%3Dclip%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(min-width%3A%201466px)%20754px%2C%20(max-width%3A%20599px)%20100vw%2C%20(min-width%3A%20600px)%20600px%2C%20237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A