Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fopposition-delegation-meets-manipur-governor-anusuiya-uikey-seeks-meeting-with-pm-modi-to-address-crisis%2Fcid%2F1980747%5C%22%3Ememorandum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20said%20that%20the%20conflict%20which%20is%20over%20six%20months%20old%20now%20has%20caused%20huge%20loss%20of%20lives%2C%20property%20and%20displacement%20of%20over%2060%2C000%20people%20belonging%20to%20both%20the%20communities.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20living%20conditions%20of%20the%20internally%20displaced%20people%20in%20relief%20camps%20is%20%E2%80%9Cinhuman%20and%20far%20from%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20instances%20of%20sporadic%20killing%2C%20firing%20and%20kidnapping%20of%20people%20including%20students%2C%20thereby%20leaving%20the%20people%20in%20great%20tension%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20hardships%20especially%20to%20those%20living%20on%20the%20periphery%2Fborders%20between%20hills%20and%20valleys.%20The%20social%20and%20economic%20lives%20of%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20have%20been%20uprooted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20parties%20said%20that%20the%20peace%20committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20not%20done%20%E2%80%9Cany%20visible%20work%E2%80%9D%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20harmony%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%2C%20a%20viable%20solution%20to%20the%20conflict%20can%20only%20be%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20We%20consider%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20India%20is%20the%20only%20hope%20for%20bringing%20peace%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20who%20has%20not%20visited%20strife%20torn%20Manipur%20in%20the%20six%20months%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20faced%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties%20for%20not%20speaking%20on%20the%20issue.%20On%20August%2010%2C%20the%20second%20last%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebroke%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20while%20replying%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20moved%20against%20his%20government.%20However%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20that%20lasted%20around%202%20hours%2020%20mins%2C%20Modi%20spoke%20about%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-as-violence-rages-on-mlas-divided-over-whether-or-not-to-hold-special-assembly-session%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20violence%20hit-state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-gives-mizoram-election-rally-a-miss-is-manipur-mayhem-the-reason%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egave%20a%20miss%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20campaigning%20in%20election%20bound%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20%E2%80%93%20the%20one%20state%20election%20where%20the%20prime%20minister%20did%20not%20go%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20also%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20defended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20its%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20and%20claimed%20that%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20cooperating%20with%20the%20Union%20so%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20remove%20him%20from%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.