F19122503%2FUttarkashi_city_WTK20150914-DSC_0003.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20rescuers%20make%20their%20way%20slowly%2C%20painfully%20to%20bring%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%5C%22%3E41%20workers%20trapped%20in%20the%20Silkyara%20Barkot%20tunnel%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20construction%20in%20Uttarkashi%20region%2C%20the%20locals%20are%20holding%20special%20ritualistic%20%3Cem%3Epooja%20%3C%2Fem%3E(prayers)%20to%20propitiate%20the%20local%20deity%20Baba%20Baukh%20Nag%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20guardian%20of%20these%20hills.%20Folks%20in%20Uttarkashi%20told%20a%20correspondent%20from%20a%20Hindi%20TV%20channel%20that%20the%20construction%20company%20had%20demolished%20a%20small%20shrine%20of%20the%20deity%20when%20they%20began%20drilling.%20This%20has%20angered%20the%20deity%20and%20resulted%20in%20the%20tragedy%20and%20brought%20%3Cem%3Evipatti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(calamity)%20on%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20team.%20The%20priest%2C%20Ganesh%20Prasad%20Bijalwan%2C%20told%20the%20channel%20that%20when%20company%20officials%20were%20apprised%20of%20this%2C%20they%20asked%20for%20the%20special%20pooja%20to%20Babbbba%20Baukh%20Nag%20%2C%20apologised%20and%20promised%20to%20build%20another%20shrine%20to%20him%20nearby.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20337px)%2085vw%2C%20337px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22337%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22411%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20project%20to%20widen%20three%20all%20weather%20roads%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Rishikesh%20to%20Mana%2C%20Rishikesh%20to%20Gangotri%20and%20Tanakpur%20to%20Pithoragarh.%20This%20covers%20the%20famous%20Char%20Dham%20Yatra%20route%20that%20links%20four%20holy%20spots%20high%20up%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Gangotri%2C%20Yamunotri%2C%20Badrinath%20and%20Kedarnath%20shrines.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20planners%20said%20that%20a%20widening%20of%20the%20roads%20with%20shoulders%20in%20the%20hilly%20terrain%20would%20facilitate%20movement%20of%20the%20army%20to%20border%20regions%20as%20well%20as%20reduce%20accidents%20and%20travel%20time%20for%20pilgrims%20undertaking%20the%20Char%20Dham%20Yatra%20all%20through%20the%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETourism%20promotion%20has%20been%20a%20big%20development%20mantra%20in%20the%20state%20since%202014.%20And%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20has%20been%20raking%20in%20huge%20revenues%20from%20tourists%20who%20have%20been%20thronging%20here.%20Even%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20held%20the%20Ardh%20Kumbh%20festival%20and%20thousands%20paid%20with%20their%20lives%20after%20they%20caught%20the%20disease%20during%20the%20holy%20%3Cem%3Esnaan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(bath).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20poor%20and%20cash%20stripped%20area%2C%20the%20locals%20were%20quick%20to%20buy%20the%20Dev%20Bhumi%20narrative%20because%20it%20brought%20in%20tourists%20with%20deep%20pockets.%20A%20major%20English%20daily%20reported%20that%20in%202022%20alone%2C%20close%20to%205%20crore%20tourists%20visited%20the%20state%20along%20with%203.8%20crore%20%3Cem%3EKanwad%20Yatris%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20all%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20roads%20and%20constant%20load%20on%20its%20scarce%20water%20resources%20began%20to%20result%20in%20ecological%20tragedies%20and%20increasing%20road%20accidents%20from%20Chamoli%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20Nainital%20to%20Mussoorie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685350%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%2F%5C%22%3EWho%20Was%20Building%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%20That%20Collapsed%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20November%205%2C%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel%20that%20would%20connect%20Silkyara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20and%20also%20joined%20the%20route%20for%20the%20Chardham%20Yatra%2C%20suddenly%20collapsed%20in%20a%20landslide.%20Apparently%20the%20mountain%20they%20were%20boring%20into%20was%20fragile%20and%20rocks%2C%20pebbles%20and%20boulders%20came%20crashing%20down%20before%20plastering%20work%20could%20be%20undertaken.%20The%20authorities%20can%20not%20say%20they%20were%20caught%20totally%20unaware.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202018%2C%20geologists%20and%20NGOs%20working%20to%20save%20the%20environment%20had%20been%20regularly%20warning%20the%20government%20about%20the%20feasibility%20of%20undertaking%20a%20mega%20project%20that%20required%20felling%20of%20trees%2C%20building%20of%20tunnels%20and%20disturbing%20the%20age%20old%20ecosystems%20in%20the%20hilly%20region.%20They%20felt%20it%20would%20pose%20a%20serious%20hazard%20to%20the%20delicate%20ecology%20of%20the%20entire%20Himalayan%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20always%20the%20matter%20was%20then%20put%20before%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20created%20a%2022-member%20High%20Powered%20Committee.%C2%A0%20However%2C%20in%20their%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fchar-dham-supreme-court-panel-head-protests-mod-remarks-7193166%2F%5C%22%3E%20July%202020%20report%2C%20the%20committee%20presented%20two%20conflicting%20viewpoints%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20from%20the%20majority%20of%2018%20members%20(14%20out%20of%20whom%20were%20reported%20to%20be%20bureaucrats)%20favoured%20the%20project%2C%20but%20four%20members%20put%20in%20their%20dissenting%20views%20firmly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20them%2C%20given%20the%20ecology%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20disaster%20resilient%20roads%20were%20more%20important%20than%20wider%20roads.%20Widening%20roads%20and%20building%20tunnels%20under%20mountains%20meant%20felling%20of%20trees%2C%20use%20of%20dynamite%20as%20well%20as%20sizeable%20and%20hard%20to%20dispose%20mounds%20of%20rubble.%20All%20these%20might%20trigger%20destructive%20and%20frequent%20landslides%20during%20rains%20and%20floods%20in%20the%20mountains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20930w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x162.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684633%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20mouth%20of%20the%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40Delhiite_%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20local%20NGO%2C%20Citizens%20for%20Green%20Doon%2C%20also%20underscored%20this%20view%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20if%20the%20Indian%20army%20was%20okay%20with%20the%20existing%20layout%20and%20width%20of%20the%20roads%2C%20risking%20ecological%20disasters%20merely%20for%20Char%20Dham%20Yatra%20was%20not%20advisable.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarkashi%20collapsed%2C%20the%20town%20of%20Joshimath%20was%20already%20sinking%2C%20revealing%20the%20unsteady%20ground%20underneath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20tunnel%20collapsed%2C%20the%20smaller%20machines%20on%20the%20site%20proved%20to%20be%20inadequate%20to%20bore%20through%20the%20rubble%20and%20rocks%20to%20retrieve%20trapped%20workers.%20By%20now%20almost%2070%25%20of%20the%20work%20is%20complete%2C%20but%20hesitation%20about%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20has%20forced%20the%20state%20government%20to%20re%20evaluate%20the%20project.%20And%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9CAmerican%E2%80%9D%20machines%20are%20being%20flown%20in%2C%20around%2050%20meters%20of%20solid%20rubble%20stand%20between%20the%20crew%20and%20the%20trapped%20workers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hill%20folk%20have%20worshipped%20nature%20like%20all%20tribals%20and%20to%20them%20the%20local%20gods%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20control%20the%20seasons%20and%20the%20ecology.%20Angering%20them%20can%20be%20disastrous%20as%20they%20do%20not%20like%20their%20hills%20being%20disfigured.%20As%20an%20example%2C%20the%20locals%20site%20the%20lore%20of%20Dronagiri%2C%20a%20hard%20to%20access%20village%20(the%2045-km%20bus%20ride%20from%20Joshimath%20to%20Jumma%20has%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20tedious%208-km%20trek).%20Dronagiri%20is%20home%20to%20some%20400%20Bhotiya%20families%20who%20migrate%20during%20the%20severe%20winters%2C%20to%20villages%20down%20below.%20The%20area%20measuring%205.5%20kms%20has%20at%20least%20500%20glaciers%20like%20Bagini%2C%20Changbang%20and%20Neeti%2C%20and%20attracts%20a%20host%20of%20folk%20from%20outside%20during%20summers%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20gatherers%20of%20rare%20herbs%20and%20hunters%20looking%20(illegally)%20to%20hunt%20the%20musk%20deer%20and%20Himalayan%20bear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-rescue-40-workers-trapped-drilling-work-halted%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%20Tunnel%20Rescue%3A%2040%20Workers%20Trapped%20for%206%20Days%2C%20Drilling%20Halted%2C%20New%20Machine%20to%20Arrive%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20they%20tell%20you%2C%20how%20since%20the%20%3Cem%3ETreta%20Yug%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20not%20only%20mortal%20kings%20but%20even%20demi%20gods%20have%20been%20punished%20for%20ravaging%20these%20hills.%20According%20to%20legends%2C%20during%20the%20battle%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Hanuman%20had%20brought%20the%20miracle%20plant%20(%3Cem%3Esanjivani%20booti%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20revive%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20brother.%20But%20since%20he%20inadvertently%20destroyed%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20holy%20mountain%20(Parvat%20Dev)%2C%20causing%20its%20disfigurement%2C%C2%A0%20Hanuman%20still%20remains%20unforgiven.%20At%20the%20formal%20celebration%20of%20Jagar%20in%20the%20village%2C%20when%20the%20%3Cem%3Eatma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(spirit)%20of%20the%20Dev%20Parbat%20appears%20in%20the%20body%20of%20a%20medium%20(known%20as%20Pashuwa)%20amid%20chanting%20of%20prayers%2C%20the%20right%20arm%20(symbolic%20of%20the%20right%20flank%20of%20the%20Drongiri%20hill)%20hangs%20limp%20and%20lifeless%20till%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20Local%20Parbat%20Devta%20departs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%20Baba%20Baukhnag%20Devta%20protect%20the%20hapless%20workers%20while%20the%20rescue%20work%20goes%20on%20using%2C%20as%20the%20media%20was%20assured%20by%20the%20highest%20authorities%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98New%20Austrian%20Tunnelling%20Method%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20combination%20of%20drill%20and%20blast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700377185000%2C%22v