%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Perfect%20Winter%20Getaway%3A%208%20Himalayan%20Homestays%20You%20Can%20Snuggle%20In%20to%20Enjoy%20Snowfall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20states%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20temperatures%20soar%20to%20an%20unbearable%2045%20degrees%2C%20snow%20was%20an%20enigma%20for%20me.%20I%20would%20often%20watch%20it%20captured%20on%20television%20and%20wonder%20how%20it%20would%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20father%2C%20who%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20young%20adult%20life%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171576%2Fias-academy-lbsnaa-mussoorie-ganga-dhaba-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Mussoorie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20often%20narrate%20how%20magical%20the%20experience%20is.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20certain%20music%20in%20the%20air%20when%20the%20snow%20starts%20to%20fall.%E2%80%9D%20Lost%20in%20his%20vivid%20narration%2C%20my%20mother%20would%20pull%20me%20out%20of%20my%20wonderland%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20the%20most%20fortunate%20ones%20get%20to%20witness%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20must%20be%20the%20%E2%80%98most%20fortunate%E2%80%99%20because%2C%20after%20nearly%20four%20to%20five%20failed%20attempts%20of%20trying%20to%20be%20at%20the%20right%20hill%20station%20at%20the%20wrong%20time%20or%20missing%20it%20by%20just%20a%20week%2C%20I%20was%20finally%20able%20to%20witness%20the%20beauty%20of%20snow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20never%20experienced%20the%20magic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276152%2Fkangsing-snow-ice-sculpture-association-ladakh-workshop-pics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20fresh%20snow%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20if%20you%E2%80%