all%20but%20vanishing%20in%20front%20of%20his%20eyes.%20He%20felt%20disheartened%20that%20his%20hometown%20was%20also%20becoming%20like%20a%20big%20city%2C%20devoid%20of%20its%20natural%20beauty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20tragic%20incident%20changed%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20computer%20science%20graduate%E2%80%99s%20life.%20His%20older%20brother%2C%20Sridhar%2C%20died%20in%20an%20accident%2C%20leaving%20Srikanth%20to%20move%20back%20home.%20He%20started%20working%20in%20the%20fields%20with%20his%20father%2C%20a%20farmer.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20his%20dream%2C%20to%20increase%20the%20green%20cover%20of%20his%20hometown.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20by%20planting%201%2C000%20trees%20in%202018%2C%20today%20the%2034-year-old%20has%20planted%20over%2015%2C000%20trees%20in%20Vellore%2C%20creating%20three%20forests.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20he%20has%20faced%20threats%20by%20the%20land%20mafia%20and%20politicians%2C%20had%20his%20trees%20cut%2C%20been%20beaten%2C%20but%20nothing%20has%20shaken%20him.%20He%20stands%20firmly%20on%20his%20resolve%20that%20he%20is%20giving%20back%20to%20Mother%20Nature%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%2C%20come%20what%20may.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20a%2025-acre%20barren%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20transformed%20a%2025%20acre%20land%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2